fields.name: Bill McKibben
fields.about: Bill McKibben is the author of ten books, including The End of Nature, The Age of Missing Information, and Enough: Staying Human in an Engineered Age. A former staff writer for The New Yorker, he writes regularly for Harperâ€™s, The Atlantic Monthly, and The New York Review of Books, among other publications. He is a scholar in residence at Middlebury College and lives in Vermont with his wife, the writer Sue Halpern, and their daughter.

fields.content:
Restore Permanently Deleted Files

If you fail to restore a deleted file within the 30-day window, or if you have emptied the trash manually, the files will be permanently deleted from your Google Drive.

You can however contact Google Support and they may restore the deleted files for you.

  1. Go to support.google.com/drive?p=file_recovery and sign-in with the Google account you used to delete the file.

  2. Provide your first name, last name, and check the consent box to confirm that you are trying to recover files you deleted from Google Drive.

You’ll receive an email from drive-noreply@google.com confirming that your request has been received and that it may take up to 48 hours for the files to be restored. (It usually takes less than 12 hours.)

Google recommends that you avoid emptying your trash while the file recovery process is ongoing. Also, please note that files that you have yourself uploaded to Google Drive may be recovered in this process. If you are not the owner of a file, it cannot be restored through this process.

Once the restoration process is complete, Google Support will send you another email confirming that the files have been restored. You can now open your Google Drive and the permanently deleted files and folders will be visible in their original location.

fields.name: Mathematics Textbook
fields.description: The "Mathematics Book" is an educational resource designed for Montessori children. It is filled with a variety of activities and exercises that are specifically tailored to help young children develop essential math skills such as numbers recognition, counting, addition and subtraction. The book features hands-on exercises and interactive puzzles that are designed to be fun and engaging for children, while also helping them to learn important math concepts in a concrete way. Some of the activities included in the book are counting exercises, matching numbers and quantities, and simple problem-solving exercises. The book is suitable for children ages 3-6 and comes in a durable, easy-to-use format that is perfect for both at-home and classroom use. The book is aligned with the Montessori method of education and will be a great addition to any Montessori curriculum, it will help children to develop a strong foundation in math.

fields.name: Stories & Rhymes
fields.description: The "Stories & Rhymes Book" is a collection of engaging and age-appropriate stories and rhymes designed for Montessori children. It is filled with a variety of tales that are specifically tailored to help young children develop essential skills such as reading comprehension, imagination, and critical thinking. The book features a wide range of stories that include folktales, fairy tales, and classic children's stories. The stories are designed to be fun and engaging for children, while also helping them to learn important values such as kindness, honesty, and responsibility. The book is suitable for children ages 3-6 and comes in a durable, easy-to-use format that is perfect for both at-home and classroom use. The illustrations in the book will also help to hold children's attention and make reading even more fun. The stories will help children to develop a love for reading and imagination.

fields.name: Malayalam Textbook
fields.description: The "Malayalam Textbook" is a comprehensive educational resource for Montessori children learning the Malayalam language. It is designed to introduce young children to the Malayalam alphabet, vocabulary, and grammar in a fun and interactive way. The book features colorful illustrations and engaging exercises that are specifically tailored to help children develop their listening, speaking, reading, and writing skills in Malayalam. Some of the activities included in the book are matching exercises, fill-in-the-blank sentences, and simple stories to read and comprehend. The book is suitable for children ages 3-6 and comes in a durable, easy-to-use format that is perfect for both at-home and classroom use. The book is also aligned with the Montessori method of education and will be a great addition to any Montessori curriculum, it will help children to develop a strong foundation in Malayalam language.

fields.name: Environmental Studies
fields.description: The "Environmental Studies Textbook" is a comprehensive educational resource for Montessori children learning about the environment. It is designed to introduce young children to the basics of environmental science, including concepts such as conservation, renewable energy, and recycling, in a fun and interactive way. The book features colorful illustrations and engaging exercises that are specifically tailored to help children develop their understanding of the natural world and their role in preserving it. Some of the activities included in the book are matching exercises, fill-in-the-blank sentences, and simple stories to read and comprehend. The book is suitable for children ages 3-6 and comes in a durable, easy-to-use format that is perfect for both at-home and classroom use. The book is also aligned with the Montessori method of education and will be a great addition to any Montessori curriculum and will inspire children to develop an appreciation for the environment.

fields.name: Colouring Book
fields.description: The "Colouring Book" is a creative and educational resource designed for Montessori children. It is filled with a variety of detailed illustrations and patterns that are specifically tailored to help young children develop essential skills such as fine motor control, hand-eye coordination and concentration. The book features a wide range of illustrations that include animals, nature, shapes, patterns and more. The illustrations are designed to be fun and engaging for children, while also helping them to improve their coloring skills. The book also includes blank pages for children to create their own drawings. The book is suitable for children ages 3-6 and comes in a durable, easy-to-use format that is perfect for both at-home and classroom use.

fields.name: English Textbook
fields.description: The "English Textbook" is an essential educational resource for Montessori children learning the English language. It is designed to introduce young children to the basics of the English language, including the alphabet, vocabulary, and grammar, in a fun and interactive way. The book features colorful illustrations and engaging exercises that are specifically tailored to help children develop their listening, speaking, reading, and writing skills in English. Some of the activities included in the book are matching exercises, fill-in-the-blank sentences, and simple stories to read and comprehend. The book is suitable for children ages 3-6 and comes in a durable, easy-to-use format that is perfect for both at-home and classroom use. The book is also aligned with the Montessori method of education and will be a great addition to any Montessori curriculum.

fields.name: Hindi Textbook
fields.description: The "Hindi Textbook" is a comprehensive educational resource for Montessori children learning the Hindi language. It is designed to introduce young children to the Hindi alphabet, vocabulary, and grammar in a fun and interactive way. The book features colorful illustrations and engaging exercises that are specifically tailored to help children develop their listening, speaking, reading, and writing skills in Hindi. Some of the activities included in the book are matching exercises, fill-in-the-blank sentences, and simple stories to read and comprehend. The book is suitable for children ages 3-6 and comes in a durable, easy-to-use format that is perfect for both at-home and classroom use. The book is also aligned with the Montessori method of education and will be a great addition to any Montessori curriculum.

fields.name: Activity Book
fields.description: The "Activity Book" is an educational resource designed for Montessori children. It is filled with a variety of activities that are specifically tailored to help young children develop essential skills such as fine motor control, problem-solving, and independent thinking. The book features hands-on exercises and interactive puzzles that are designed to be fun and engaging for children, while also helping them to learn important concepts. Some of the activities included in the book are mazes, matching exercises, and cut-and-paste projects. The book is suitable for children ages 3-6 and comes in a durable, easy-to-use format that is perfect for both at-home and classroom use.

fields.title: About
fields.description:
In this highly competitive world, where some students require Individual Care and attention in order to be nurtured into a valuable member of the community. We, as a team, recognize that there are differences in learning speed among students which have no place in a classroom setting. Team INTERVAL provides personalized online and home tuition for K-12 students with one-to-one individual care and attention towards the progress of students and molds them to develop their imaginative and innovative skills.

INTERVAL was incorporated in 2021 as Sanco India Edu Solutions Pvt Ltd. This is an institution that focuses on the development and all-around progress of the Individual, at INTERVAL we believe in guiding individuals who lack the basic reading and writing skills and also those who require personal assistance to be more competitive. Our syllabus is designed according to the needs and the capabilities of each individual that we help, in their journey towards educational excellence. Our custom-made syllabuses are crafted after thorough research in the fields of pedagogy, and psychology. our classes are conducted by experienced trainers with diverse backgrounds. Trainers undergo constant knowledge enrichment programs at a regular interval in order to include the latest developments
fields.address: Sanco India Edu Solutions Pvt Ltd, Building No AP 9/535, Arakkal Complex, Puthalam, Areekode PO, Malappuram, Kerala, 673639

fields.title: Worksheets and Textbooks
fields.description:
We provide textbook series with a balanced, chronological presentation of informations according to the modern curriculums. Our Worksheets are more participative and mind provoking than any other mode of
imparting education which makes them more creative

fields.title: Value Based Education
fields.description: Value Education means teaching and learning of ideals. The aim is for students to understand moral values and show their good behavior and attitude towards society.It helps the students to develop the character and improves the inner and outer personality of the student.

fields.title: Modern Curriculam
fields.description:
The modern curriculum apart from subject or content- knowledge gives importance to provide practical experiences and knowledge to kids based on Psychology of Individual Differences through a conducive
learning environment.

fields.title: One to One
fields.description: One-to-one sessions ensures the students interacts with the teacher individually, so that each can learn and understand concepts at their own pace and in their own way and identify their full potential.

fields.title: Assessment and Evaluation
fields.description:
Well-designed assessment can encourage active learning especially when the assessment delivery is innovative and engaging. Proper tests and evaluation can benefit the student as curriculum and pace of
teaching is customized as per the results.

fields.question: Who can join the course?
fields.answer: Children who are of age between 3.5 and 7 can join the course.

fields.question: Whatâ€™s the duration of the course?
Are you teaching on a special curriculum?
fields.answer: Yes, we provide a specially prepared curriculum for the kids to understand things in a way more easier.

fields.question: How far this will benefit the kids?
fields.answer: As long as the course is just meant for the kids, it obviously makes a huge impact on their learning skills and the future.
